{
  "title": "Mildly Springy Egyptian Chinese Leaf Skillet",
  "description": "A post-workout Egyptian dish featuring Chinese leaf, with a mother-sauce-base and low-glycemic-friendly ingredients, providing a grassy and springy flavor profile.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian Chinese",
